{
  "stem": "22892.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean that's what he was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was a head hunter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He would get paid for killing a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I heard about the guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I never knew him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I never knew that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I heard in villages.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "People, you know, occasionally farmers would say things to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, there were nice people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, you've got to watch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You've got so and so looking for you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He knows there was a kid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He doesn't-- you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and that's one day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She says, he was in my house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was leaving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, they didn't look out the window to see what's going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't see it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when I told them that, they knew that that's the same I came in contact with.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What village was this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's like you know when you go out and you go by, you see a few houses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was just this-- I don't remember the name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I lost-- it's amazing that some of the villages I remembered for so long, and now I don't remember them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But just small places, they're very small, scattered houses with one road.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this went on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Same thing, I was doing the same thing, wandering and walking and, and hiding, until I came to-- this was already in the spring that I remember I came to a Czech village.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't remember that name now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think it-- and, and somebody said-- no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I came to this-- he was a head of the village, a Czech family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he asked me if I wanted to work for him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He says he doesn't want to hire any Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, well I'm not a Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, that's good.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
